Disease:     Cholera
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    Vibrio cholerae
Transmission:Contaminated water
Symptoms:    Profuse watery diarrhea, vomiting
Treatment:   Oral rehydration, antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   0.095M
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  1854

Disease:     Smallpox
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Variola
Transmission:Respiratory, contact
Symptoms:    Pockmarks, fever
Treatment:   Eradicated (1980)
Deaths/yr:   EradicatedM
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  Antiquity

============================================================
  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Transfer Learning
Category:    Technique
Definition:  Reuses pre-trained model weights for new related tasks
Year:        2009
Researchers: Pan and Yang survey
Applications:Fine-tuning LLMs, computer vision
Related:     Pre-training, fine-tuning, domain adaptation

Concept:     Word Embeddings
Category:    Representation
Definition:  Dense vectors where semantic similarity = vector proximity
Year:        2013
Researchers: Mikolov et al.
Applications:NLP, recommendation, search
Related:     Word2Vec, GloVe, BERT embeddings

Concept:     Vector Database
Category:    Infrastructure
Definition:  Stores high-dimensional embeddings for similarity search
Year:        2019
Researchers: Pinecone/Weaviate/Faiss
Applications:RAG, semantic search, recommendation
Related:     ANN search, HNSW, cosine similarity

